This topic is closely related to the field of logic and semantics, which falls under the cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the recursive definition principle, which is a topic that falls under the cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) and cs.THEORY (Theoretical Computer Science) sub-categories.
